d|2009|с=33}}<br />{{не переведено 4|Панк-рок-ривайвл|панк-рок-ривайвл|en|Punk rock#revival}}<ref name="AXS">{{cite web|url=http://www.axs.com/whether-you-call-them-pop-punk-or-rock-simple-plan-is-simply-amazing-12473|title=Whether you call them pop, punk or rock, Simple Plan is simply amazing|lang=en|publisher=AXS|author=Brittany Frederick|date=2014-06-18|accessdate=2015-03-07}}</ref><ref name="Revival">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/02/04/arts/rock-review-punk-is-back-adapted-to-more-congenial-ways.html|title=Rock Review; Punk Is Back, Adapted To More Congenial Ways.| author= Kelefa Sannen.|publisher =The New York Times|date=2003-02-04|lang=en|accessdate=2015-04-22}}</ref>
| Язык = [[английский]],<br />[[французский]]{{ref+|Группа также записала версии песен «[[Jet Lag (песня Simple Plan)|Jet Lag]]» с участием канадской певицы [[Мэри Мэй]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.edmontonjournal.com/2012/02/13/simple-plan-was-a-bit-nervous-to-release-a-french-version-of-jet-lag/|title=
