| ISSN     = 0006-2510
}}</ref>, [[The Guardian]]<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/feb/26/popandrock1| title = Simple Plan.|author= Caroline Sullivan.|publisher=[[The Guardian]]|lang=en|date=2005-02-26|accessdate=2015-04-22}}</ref>, [[BBC]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7222822.stm|title=Talking Shop: Simple Plan|publisher=BBC|lang=en|author=Fiona Pryor|date=2008-02-12|accessdate=2015-03-30}}</ref>, [[Entertainment Weekly]]<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.ew.com/article/2008/02/08/simple-plan|title=Simple Plan.|author=Simon Vozick-Levinson.|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|lang=en|date=2015-01-17|accessdate=2015-03-30}}</ref>, [[Коммерсантъ]]<ref name="Коммерсантъ">{{статья
